@node "Main" "No title"

 The DLG Pro UUCP Primer
 =======================

This archive includes information and examples that will help smooth the
path towards installing UUCP on a DLG system.

Overall, UUCP is a self-contained unit.  It imports mail, it exports it, and
it even includes a news and mail reader.  What it lacks is an interface that
lends itself easily to online environments.  This is of course DLG's forte,
but DLG itself lacks the ability to directly import and export mail to the
internet.

Combining the two is sometimes tricky, but actually quite simple provided
you know a little bit about what you're doing.  Overall, it's around as
simple to install as FidoNet and a little trickier to maintain.

